node.title: Police looking for dashcam footage in homicide investigation
node.description: Police are seeking dashcam footage that may help their investigation into a West Auckland homicide.
node.content:
["Police are seeking dashcam footage that may help their investigation into a West Auckland homicide.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "David Keith Yates was found dead at a house in Swanson on Saturday two weeks ago.", "One man has been charged with murder.", "The police want motorists who were driving along Candia, North Candia, Swanson and Pooks roads between between 7pm on Friday 12 November and 10.30am on Saturday 13 November to check for any footage."]
